Package: disprr
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Election Results and Compute Disproportionality Measures
Version: 0.1.1
Author: pierzgal
Maintainer: The package maintainer <pierzgal@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides a few functions to simulate election results, using various proportional representation algorithms to apportion seats. It also computes and plots a variaty of disproportionality measures.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: ggplot2 (>= 2.2), ggthemes (>= 3.3.0), viridis (>= 0.3.0), dplyr (>= 0.5.0), truncdist (>= 1.0-2), psych (>= 1.6.12)
